·中标麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V7
·aarch64架构:
perl、perl-CPAN、perl-ExtUtils-CBuilder、perl-ExtUtils-Embed、perl-ExtUtils-Install、perl-IO-Zlib、perl-Locale-Maketext-Simple、perl-Module-CoreList、perl-Module-Loaded、perl-Object-Accessor、perl-Package-Constants、perl-Pod-Escapes、perl-Time-Piece、perl-core、perl-devel、perl-libs、perl-macros、perl-tests
·x86_64架构:
perl、perl-CPAN、perl-ExtUtils-CBuilder、perl-ExtUtils-Embed、perl-ExtUtils-Install、perl-IO-Zlib、perl-Locale-Maketext-Simple、perl-Module-CoreList、perl-Module-Loaded、perl-Object-Accessor、perl-Package-Constants、perl-Pod-Escapes、perl-Time-Piece、perl-core、perl-devel、perl-libs、perl-macros、perl-tests
·银河麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V10
